    "text": [
        "Every human being always works hard to become financially stable and believe that money is the main reason to live a happy life. Therefore, people work hard and even do overtime to collect cash to buy goods to make their life\u2019s comfortable. Although, having a healthy life and maintaining a beautiful family also can bring happiness.",
        "A large number of individuals believe that money can buy happiness and they try to climb up the corporate ladder to become successful and ultimately can end up with a high salary with luxurious life. Since, the current market increases the quality of the products while increasing the price, a large amount of cash is needed to live a comfortable life. As an example, the value of  care can be increase when it has more features to make the owner comfortable. Therefore, mankind believes that financial stability will result to enjoy life.",
        "On the other hand,  personal health and  family play a big role in happiness. Doing regular exercise and having healthy diets will reduce the chances to get any illnesses.  As an example, having diabetes will not allow one to enjoy  life. Instead it will make the person depressed regardless the how much money in the bank account. Accordingly, a number of researchers discovered that 56% of individuals are depressed due to family issues. Hence, allocating time for your loved ones is also important to stay happy in life.",
        "In conclusion, money can play a big role in human life to maintain the pleasure of life. But on the other hand, maintaining a healthy life and a happy family will also take you to happiness along with money."
